    "title": "Identifying rate limits for Advanced Commerce APIs"
  },
  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The Advanced Commerce API limits the number of requests that you can submit to each endpoint within a specified timespan. The request limits apply per app.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "The following table lists the rate limits in the production environment, expressed in requests per second. Limits are enforced on an hourly basis.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "header": "row",
          "rows": [
            [
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Endpoint",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Rate limit (per second)",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            ],
            [
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.advancedcommerceapi/documentation/AdvancedCommerceAPI/Change-Subscription-Price",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "50",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            ],
            [
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.advancedcommerceapi/documentation/AdvancedCommerceAPI/Cancel-a-Subscription",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "5",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            ]
          ],
          "type": "table"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The rate limits in the sandbox environment are 10 percent of the limits in the table above.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "The Advanced Commerce server may make adjustments to reduce or increase these rate limits as needed at any time.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Handle-exceeded-rate-limits-gracefully",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Handle exceeded rate limits gracefully",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "If you exceed a per-hour limit, the API rejects the request with an ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "HTTP 429",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " response, with a ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.advancedcommerceapi/documentation/AdvancedCommerceAPI/RateLimitExceededError",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " in the body. Consider the following as you integrate the API:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "If you periodically call the API, throttle your requests to avoid exceeding the per-hour limit for an endpoint.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Manage the ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "HTTP 429 RateLimitExceededError",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " in your error-handling process. For example, log the failure and queue the job to process it again at a later time.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Check the ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "Retry-After",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " header if you receive the ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "HTTP 429",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " error. This header contains a UNIX time, in milliseconds, that informs you when you can next send a request.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "unorderedList"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
